{"tid":929130,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚準備同男朋友扑嘢果陣嬲到走咗","createTime":"2018-12-05T10:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T11:29:30.000Z","uid":21845,"like":10,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"757e5b5c5c9e2ad74e2c955eaa26f4371b8f6aa1","tid":929130,"uid":21845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:56:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">話說琴日男朋友生日，咁我就早啲做完公司嘢再去接佢放工，然後一齊食飯啦。<br />\n<br />\n成晩個氣氛算舒服嘅，大家都係講下近排自己公司有咩閪人閪事呀果類嘢。食完飯佢就話不如今晚上佢度瞓，又話咩想同我一齊切生日蛋糕。我心諗：你九成九係想扑嘢啦。平時我好少會去佢屋企過夜，又遠又唔近公司，不過見係佢生日咁就算啦，就當獎勵下佢。<br />\n<br />\n佢渣緊車嘅時侯已經係咁掃我隻手，又掂下我大髀邊，搞到我㷫烚烚。跟住喺佢屋企搭lift果陣佢仲要一路攬住我條腰一路磨我個pat，驚死留下看更唔知我地一陣會扑嘢咁樣。<br />\n<br />\n入到屋果陣我地已經係差唔多半裸咁濟，我一路用大髀輕輕掃佢個龜頭一路問：「套呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」佢完全冇理過我，淨係係咁摸我patpat同埋啜我耳仔。我以為佢做之前會帶返個套，所以繼續慢慢chok佢條嘢，用指甲刮下龜頭邊刺激下佢咁樣「小朋友你硬晒啦喎......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」我好細聲喺佢耳邊講。突然佢好大力噤我落張枱度，一嘢扯開我條under想插入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。我即刻轉身推開佢：「做咩啊，帶咗套先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」佢仲要笑騎騎咁話：「唔制唔制，我要後入中出你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」我話：「唔戴套唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」跟住著返條under。點知佢即刻扯晒火：「屌！男人老狗咁撚麻煩......咁想帶套你自己帶囉！比你插我囉！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」我當堂㩒咗佢一巴：「你講咩話？你有冇尊重過我？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」然後著返晒啲衫開門走<br />\n<br />\n到而家佢都完全冇搵過我，係咪代表我地玩完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></span>"},{"pid":"620b8cdd4db141258fe5a9441e8648d323641494","tid":929130,"uid":5649,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:58:27.000Z","msg":"死基佬，我睇到扯左"},{"pid":"8e13bda356993ef4abfafb7d0c820ecc4170f5df","tid":929130,"uid":27605,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:59:21.000Z","msg":"帶黎做咩又唔會有bb"},{"pid":"afb11f87a5e6efa3473f7f091e2fec7987a6e6e3","tid":929130,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:59:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"413e51629174bb34ba40460af32b6b39bbd45cd9","tid":929130,"uid":206726,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:59:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1fiVJgg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1fiVJgg.png&h=fea88fdf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3454effff06d2b991a92534d808d23b83c14a6ea","tid":929130,"uid":73024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:00:09.000Z","msg":"估撚到 好彩無除褲"},{"pid":"ef27e39bc95426e8ed9b92cb7994f3d3fe992def","tid":929130,"uid":84277,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:00:18.000Z","msg":"頭一兩次就好笑姐<br />\n依架無人笑架啦過主啦"},{"pid":"968f510ff8785318ac252652dbd8059fd01b7854","tid":929130,"uid":25635,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:00:58.000Z","msg":"又唔會有bb，咁撚煩架你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1502bd52f64ce0377b3371a842687c3d3d6b72c1","tid":929130,"uid":37796,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"8e13bda356993ef4abfafb7d0c820ecc4170f5df","tid":929130,"uid":27605,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T10:59:21.000Z","msg":"帶黎做咩又唔會有bb"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:01:07.000Z","msg":"所以基佬多愛滋唔係無原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d419f1bc129eec9abbea63d3d3bdea635e40d46","tid":929130,"uid":123053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-05T11:01:23.000Z","msg":"我肯帶套<br />\n嚟番場友誼波？"},{"pid":"88292c83df1f33c993aeb1371312c8593904380f","tid":929130,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1502bd52f64ce0377b3371a842687c3d3d6b72c1","tid":929130,"uid":37796,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quo